<td><a href="UltraBoard.cgi?Action=ShowProfile&ID=jbex&Board=paladin&Idle=30&Sort=0&Order=Descend&Page=0&Session=" target="Profile" OnMouseOver="window.status='View Jbex (jbex) Profile.';return true;" OnMouseOut="window.status=''"><font face="Verdana" size="1" color="000000 ">Profile</font></a></td><td align="RIGHT"></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="EEEEEE">
<td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="5" cellpadding="5" align="CENTER">
<tr>
<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">Warriors are more preffered in the post-50 groups. why? because palies, like all hybrids, take 125% of the xp a warrior would. That makes slower leveling for everyone. They would rather go with a pure tank. <p>

Paladins won't match a well equiped warrior in damage. Then again, a good warrior knows he's not supposed to do the most damage. He is supposed to hit frequently. Taunt skill in itself does verry little, it's the two swords in his hands that keep the mob's attention. That is why a good warrior will never use a wurmslayer.<p>

The paladin can still taunt better then a warrior in some instances. A decent 1h with low delay, bash, stuns, and root will make sure the mob stays interested in you. <p>

It makes little difference if the best war or pally 1h is better. That extra 0.5 dmg ratio makes no difference since the warrior wields two of them.<p>

In general, a nice dmg weapon is nice but all you really need is something good enough to let you taunt. Concentrate on ac/hp. Especially into the 40's hp begins to matter since every extra point you get makes the complete heal that much more efficient. Forget the two hander, get a decent 1hs and a shield. The exra ac is important, especially when you are pulling. Not to mention the stats. <p>

Personally I think the Fiery Avenger is ... inadequate. The only reason I might consider attempting to get it is as a status symbol. If we are talking of weapons of this calliber, I would much rather have a Sarnak Battle Shield and Sword of the Morning, or at least Stave of Shielding or a Darkmetal Holy Water Sprinkler. I only pray and ask Brell that the new epic paly weapon that has not been found yet is one handed.<p>

Jbex Soulbreach<br>
Sworn servant of Brell<br>
44th circle</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr bgcolor="DDDDDD">
