Barbarian Warrior-Can bash without a shield and can use a Wurmslayer with perhaps another 1hder(better get that Stamina up ladies and gents), Higher HP which mean you take more damage, Clerics purpose is to heal, Pallies only get unwanted cleric spells for that lvl,I mean really what is minor healing gonna do at lvl 9?<p>

Human Paladin-Can't duel wield, low str so kiss thopse heavy armor pieces good bye, they have spells but clerics cast them better(mind you this means at lower lvls and with more mana), you find out that extra 200hp bonus you put on don't mean jack when the mob hits for 100+ in a hit and double attacks.<p>

Those are just a few pros and cons Pallies can eventually deal more dmg but by that time warriors get the coolest disciplines to help them but can't take the damage, warriors can deal what they take which is stated in the books with the game.But just play what you want don't let me influence you.<p>

